description: Beautifully updated 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath duplex located on the desirable East Side of South Boston. Nestled within a charming 2-family building, this 1,070+ sq ft home offers the feel of a single-family residence, complete with a large private patio and second-floor deck—perfect for entertaining or relaxing in the sun. Inside, the home boasts thoughtful updates and timeless character, including refinished wide plank pine hardwood floors, enhanced trim detailing, and custom built-in closets. The upgraded kitchen features sleek quartz countertops, a large custom island, and brand-new Frigidaire stainless steel appliances, making it a true chef’s delight. Additional comforts include central heat and AC, in-unit laundry, and extra storage. Ideally situated just blocks from the beach, with easy access to Southie's vibrant restaurant and shopping scene, public transportation, and major highways. Don’t miss your chance to own this turnkey home in one of Boston’s most sought-after neighborhoods
